    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Perhaps a better solution to your problem would be to use a mask based off of the index values, so:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nmask = index.get_level_values('year') == 2010\r\ntrain = series[mask]\r\ntest = series[~mask]\r\n```"
