    "created_at": "2018-08-14T19:40:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-08-14T19:40:05Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks @WillAyd, that syntax works identically for both Series and DataFrame, which is exactly what I was looking for.\r\n\r\nAt the same time, I think supporting different methods for Series and DataFrame makes it very confusing for new users (like myself). When I searched for how to do this with a MultiIndex, the `query` method was the first answer I found. It worked great for splitting my data (DataFrame) but didn't work for splitting my labels (Series). Are you also proposing we drop `query` from DataFrames because the same thing _could_ be done through other methods?"
  },
